le|color={{beauty color}}|area=Event: \'\'[[Special Stages#Great Challenge|Bellossom Appears]]\'\'}}\n{{Availability/Entry1|1|v=Rumble World|color={{fire color}}|area=[[Leafy Expanse#Royal Garden|Leafy Expanse: Royal Garden]] <small>(All Areas)</small>}}\n|}\n|}\n{{Availability/Footer}}\n\n===Stats===\n====Base stats====\n=====Generation II-V=====\n{{BaseStats|\ntype=grass|\nHP=75|\nAttack=80|\nDefense=85|\nSpAtk=90|\nSpDef=100|\nSpeed=50}}\n\n=====Generation VI onward=====\n{{BaseStats|\ntype=grass|\nHP=75|\nAttack=80|\nDefense=95|\nSpAtk=90|\nSpDef=100|\nSpeed=50}}\n\n====Pokéathlon stats====\n{{Pokéthlon\n|type=grass\n|Speed=3\n|SpeedMax=4\n|Power=2\n|PowerMax=3\n|Technique=4\n|TechniqueMax=5\n|Stamina=3\n|StaminaMax=3\n|Jump=3\n|JumpMax=4\n}}\n\n===Type effectiveness===\n{{TypeEffectiveness|\ntype1=grass|\nNormal=  100 |\nFighting=100 |\nFlying=  200 |\nPoison=  200 |\nGround=   50 |\nRock=    100 |\nBug=     200 |\nGhost=   100 |\nSteel=   100 |\n\nFire=    200 |\nWater=    50 |\nGrass=    50 |\nElectric= 50 |\nPsychic= 100 |\nIce=     200 |\nDragon=  100 |\nDark=    100 |\nFairy=   100}}\n\n===Learnset===\n====By [[Level|leveling up]]====\n{{learnlist/levelh/7|Bellossom|Grass|Grass|2}}\n{{learnlist/level7|1|Magical Leaf|Grass|Special|60|&mdash;|20||\'\'\'}}\n{{learnlist/level7|1|Leaf Storm|Grass|Special|130|90|5||\'\'\'}}\n{{learnlist/level7|1|Leaf Blade|Grass|Physical|90|100|15||\'\'\'}}\n{{learnlist/level7|1|Mega Drain|Grass|Special|40|100|15||\'\'\'}}\n{{learnlist/level7|1|Sweet Scent|Normal|Status|&mdash;|100|20}}\n{{learnlist/level7|1|Stun Spore|Grass|Status|&mdash;|75|30}}\n{{learnlist/level7|1|Sunny Day|Fire|Status|&mdash;|&mdash;|5}}\n{{learnlist/level7|{{tt|Evo.|Learned upon evolving}}|Magical Leaf|Grass|Special|60|&mdash;|20||\'\'\'}}\n{{learnlist/level7|39|Quiver Dance|Bug|Status|&mdash;|&mdash;|20}}\n{{learnlist/level7|49|Petal Blizzard|Grass|Physical|90|100|15||\'\'\'}}\n{{learnlist/level7|59|Petal Dance|Grass|Special|120|100|10||\'\'\'}}\n{{learn